html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="utf-8")
    meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no")
    title iTutor-A informal letter
    link(rel="icon" href="../itutor/iTutor.ico" type='image/x-icon')
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/frameworks/bootstrap.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/frameworks/font-awesome.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/itutor/style.css")
    script(src="/javascripts/frameworks/jquery.min.js")
    script(src="/javascripts/frameworks/bootstrap.min.js")
  body
    #paragraphs
      .container
        .panel.panel-info(style="width: 1000px;")
          .panel-heading(style="color:darkslategrey")
            | Click on the error in the blue text. Then type the correct words in the input field
      .container
        .panel.panel-default(style="width: 1000px; padding: 0px 30px 41px 30px;")
          h1.panel.panel-info(style="width:300px; padding-left:30px; background-color:rgb(191, 211, 204);") A informal letter
          p#p1.p
            | How are you? I'm very well.  
            span#1.keys I'm
            |   in Dublin for two weeks now. I'm studying at a language school. My host family are Mr and Mrs Kendall.
          p#p2.p 
            span#2.keys They
            |   both very nice. Mr Kendall teaches in a school.
          p#p3.p
            | I study in the morning with my teacher, Ann. We 
            span#3.keys aren't
            |   get too much homework.
          p#p4.p
            | In the afternoons I go sightseeing. Dublin is more exciting 
            span#4.keys that
            |  my town.
          p#p5.p
            | There are lots of places to visit. I like modern art, so I 
            span#5.keys visit often
            |   galleries and museums. I've met a girl named Martina. She's from Spain. We watched a film together last night.
          p#p6.p
            | Why  
            span#6.keys not you 
            | come to Dublin for a weekend? Write to me soon. Love, Kati.
      #image
        img.img-rounded(src="/images/itutor/1.jpg")
      #inputs
        input#guess.input(type="text" placeholder="Type the correct word")
        #wrong
        button#checker.btn(type="submit") Check Answer
      #result
    // Modal content
    .container
      button#myBtn.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(type="button" style="display:none;") Open Modal
      #myModal.modal.fade(role="dialog")
        .modal-dialog
          .modal-content
            .modal-header
              button.close(type="button" data-dismiss="modal") Ã—
              h2.modal-title iTUTOR says
            .modal-body
              p(style="color:'#449d44';") Congratulation. You have finished.
            .modal-footer
              button.btn.btn-default(type="button" onclick="ClaerBlur()" data-dismiss="modal") Close
    footer#footer
      span.fa.fa-spin
        img(src="/images/itutor/iTutor.ico" width="16px" height="16px")
      span iTutor

    script(src="/javascripts/itutor/lib.js")
